'''Jehad Abdullatif Ahmed Thakri''' ({{langx|ar|جهاد ذكري}}; born 21 July 2001) is a [[Saudi Arabia]]n [[football (soccer)|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Al-Qadsiah FC|Al-Qadsiah]] and the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]].<ref>{{cite web |title=جهاد عبداللطيف ذكري - Jahad Thakri |url=https://www.kooora.com/?player=145316}}</ref><ref name="soccerway">{{cite web |title=JEHAD ABDULLATIF |url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/jehad-abdullatif-ahm/691364/}}</ref>

==Career==
Thakri started his career at the youth teams of [[Al-Qadsiah FC|Al-Qadsiah]]. On 5 November 2020, Thakri signed his first professional contract with Al-Qadsiah.<ref>{{cite web |title="القادسية" يوقع 10 عقود احترافية مع "شبابه" |date=5 November 2020 |url=https://akhbaar24.argaam.com/article/detail/518288}}</ref> He made his first-team debut on 23 February 2021 in the league match against [[Al-Batin FC|Al-Batin]].<ref>{{cite web |title=AL BATIN VS. AL-QADSIAH 2 – 2 |url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2021/02/23/saudi-arabia/pro-league/al-baten/al-quadisiya-khobar/3443270/}}</ref>

